  <brief_title>Macular Retinoschisis and Detachment Associated With Glaucomatous Optic Neuropathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Macular Retinoschisis and Detachment Associated With Glaucomatous Optic Neuropathy But Without Optic Disc Pit Nor High Myopia</official_title>
